<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Hesap360 | Kredi, Mevduat ve Limit Analizi</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --bg: #020617; --surface: #0f172a; --primary: #3b82f6; --text: #f8fafc; --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08); }
        body { background: var(--bg); font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', sans-serif; color: var(--text); margin: 0; background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 50% -20%, #1e40af33 0%, transparent 50%); min-height: 100vh; }
        .container { max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
        nav { padding: 30px 0; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; }
        .logo { font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: -1px; }
        .logo span { color: var(--primary); }
        .hero { padding: 80px 0; text-align: center; }
        .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .hero h1 span { color: var(--primary); }
        .main-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr)); gap: 25px; margin-top: 50px; }
        .card { background: var(--surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 45px; border-radius: 32px; text-decoration: none; color: inherit; transition: 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275); position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
        .card:hover { border-color: var(--primary); transform: translateY(-10px); box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.5); }
        .card i { font-size: 2.5rem; color: var(--primary); margin-bottom: 25px; display: block; }
        .card h3 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
        .card p { color: #94a3b8; line-height: 1.6; }
        footer { padding: 60px 0; text-align: center; color: #64748b; font-size: 0.8rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 80px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav><a href="/" class="logo">HESAP<span>360</span></a></nav>
        <header class="hero">
            <h1>Finansal Geleceğini<br><span>Profesyonelce</span> Yönet.</h1>
            <p>Banka rasyoları ve 2026 güncel verileriyle tam isabet analizler.</p>
        </header>
        <div class="main-grid">
            <a href="/kredi" class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-building-columns"></i>
                <h3>Kredi Analizi</h3>
                <p>En uygun faiz oranlarını karşılaştırın ve ödeme planınızı oluşturun.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/kredi-limit" class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-gauge-high"></i>
                <h3>Limit Tahmini</h3>
                <p>Banka politikalarına göre çekebileceğiniz maksimum kredi tutarı.</p>
            </a>
            <a href="/mevduat" class="card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i>
                <h3>Mevduat Faizi</h3>
                <p>Birikimlerinizin net getirisini ve stopaj oranlarını hesaplayın.</p>
            </a>
        </div>
        <footer>© 2026 Hesap360 | Finansal Analiz Teknolojileri</footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
